Title:
			公告ID：KYSA-202207-1016
公告摘要：rsyslog安全漏洞
安全等级：Important
发布日期：2022年07月19日
影响CVE：CVE-2022-24903
		
1. 修复的CVE·CVE-2022-24903描述：Adiscon Rsyslog是德国Adiscon公司的一个用于收集系统日志的库。Adiscon Rsyslog之前版本存在安全漏洞，该漏洞源于使用八位字节计数的帧时，用于接收 TCP 系统日志的模块会出现堆缓冲区溢出，攻击者利用该漏洞可以破坏堆值，导致数据完整性和可用性。2. 受影响的软件包·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP2aarch64架构:rsyslog、rsyslog-help、rsyslog-hiredis、rsyslog-kafka、rsyslog-mmkubernetes、rsyslog-mmnormalize、rsyslog-mongodb、rsyslog-omamqp1、rsyslog-pgsql、rsyslog-rabbitmq、rsyslog-relpx86_64架构:rsyslog、rsyslog-help、rsyslog-hiredis、rsyslog-kafka、rsyslog-mmkubernetes、rsyslog-mmnormalize、rsyslog-mongodb、rsyslog-omamqp1、rsyslog-pgsql、rsyslog-rabbitmq、rsyslog-relp3. 软件包修复版本·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP2rsyslog-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-help-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-hiredis-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-kafka-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-mmkubernetes-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-mmnormalize-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-mongodb-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-omamqp1-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-pgsql-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-rabbitmq-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10rsyslog-relp-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky104. 修复方法方法一：配置源进行升级安装1. 打开软件包源配置文件，根据仓库地址进行修改。仓库源地址： 银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP2aarch64:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/x86_64:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/2. 配置完成后执行更新命令进行升级，命令如下：yum update Packagename方法二：下载安装包进行升级安装通过软件包地址下载软件包，使用软件包升级命令根据受影响的软件包列表进行升级安装,命令如下：yum install Packagename3. 升级完成后是否需要重启服务或操作系统：·CVE-2022-24903：无需重启操作系统与服务即可使漏洞修复生效。5. 软件包下载地址·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10 SP2rsyslog（aarch64）软件包下载地址:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-help-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.noarch.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-hiredis-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-kafka-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-mmkubernetes-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-mmnormalize-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-mongodb-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-omamqp1-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-pgsql-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-rabbitmq-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/aarch64/Packages/rsyslog-relp-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.aarch64.rpmrsyslog（x86_64）软件包下载地址:https://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-help-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.noarch.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-hiredis-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-kafka-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-mmkubernetes-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-mmnormalize-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-mongodb-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-omamqp1-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-pgsql-8.2006.0-2.p03.ky10.x86_64.rpmhttps://update.cs2c.com.cn/NS/V10/V10SP2/os/adv/lic/updates/x86_64/Packages/rsyslog-rabbitmq-8.2006.0-2.p